headline: A Stellar Stay: Spend a Night Under the Stars with Dr. Matt Agnew in Booking.com's Cosmic Cabin
summary: Booking.com has teamed up with former Bachelor and scientist Dr Matt Agnew to host a sleepover under the stars as the annual Eta Aquariids meteor shower shoots across Australian skies. One lucky pair of Genius members will enjoy an out-of-this-world experience learning about the cosmic event from the astro-expert in 'The Booking.com Cosmic Cabin', a remote home stay on the Tasman Peninsula.
